machine_model.name: Anycubic Predator
machine_model.author: ksihota
machine_model.machine_end_gcode:
M104 S0 ;extruder heater off 
M140 S0 ;heated bed heater off 
G91 ;relative positioning 
G92 E0 ;zero the extruded length 
G1 E-2 F300 ;retract the filament a bit before lifting the nozzle, to release some of the pressure 
G92 E0 ;zero the extruded length 
;M107 ;fan off 
G1 Z+0.5 E-5 ;move Z up a bit and retract filament even more 
;G1 X0.0 Y0.0 Z455.0 F4500 
G28 ;Home all axes (max endstops) 
G90 ;absolute positioning 
;M109 S60 ; wait for extruder temp to drop to 60 
;M84 ;steppers off 
;M81 ;turn off printer
machine_model.machine_start_gcode:
G21 ;metric values 
G90 ;absolute positioning 
M82 ;set extruder to absolute mode 
M107 ;start with the fan off 
G28 ;Home 
G1 Z15.0 F1000;short move 
G92 E0 ;zero the extruded length 
G1 F200 E3 ;extrude 3mm of feed stock adjust so I don't have to remove any filament 
G92 E0 ;zero the extruded length again 
G1 F4000 ;move to bed 
;Put printing message on LCD screen 
M117 Printing... 
;G5; this is in order to resume on Power failure (only works on SD prints)
